channel.description:
Hi,

is there any way we can refresh state that we set from frontity.settings.js?

where the settings are : 

```
{

      "name": "@frontity/wp-source",

      "state": {

        "source": {
"postTypes": [

            {

              "type": "custom",

              "endpoint": "custom",

              "archive": "/custom",

            },
}
```


are we able to?
